OL,4,CMustard gas among toxic waste in Wales'
OL,5,Cold landfill sites
OL,6, Toxic waste including mustard gas is
OL,7, buried among more than 1,500 disused
OL,8, landfill sites across Wales.
OL,10,FEnvironmental campaigners Greenpeace
OL,11,Fbranded the 1,572 locations "ticking
OL,12,Ftime bombs".
OL,14,FNatural Resources Wales (NRW) data
OL,15,Freveals hundreds of the sites contain
OL,16,Fhazardous waste and only a few dozen
OL,17,Fare protectively lined.
OL,19,FThe organisation said it worked with
OL,20,Fcouncils to ensure old landfills were
OL,21,Fnot a pollution risk.
